## Envio (Rootstream) environment variables
## Copy to `.env` if you want to use shell env overrides instead of editing config.yaml.
##
## On Windows: run Envio in WSL/Linux. The Envio CLI binary is not available for native win32 in some releases.

# Rootstream contract address (Rootstock testnet, chain id 31)
ROOTSTREAM_ADDRESS=0x491dd3A88BfdBB066dE19c2ADa32F2D864bf7b6A

# Rootstock testnet RPC URL used by config.yaml (sync)
ROOTSTOCK_TESTNET_RPC_URL=https://public-node.testnet.rsk.co

